latestIgtvVideos.title: Thankyou Covid warriors 🩺🙏🏻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The medical industry, our covid warriors are working day in and day out , selflessly  to help fight covid. Be it a doctor, an intern a technician, or the hospital cleaners. To say the least, what they’re doing is not easy!!
It is of paramount importance that they receive nothing but our gratitude, support and love. 
These are veryyyy tough times and it’s understandable for someone to lash out at a doctor or behave in a way that isn’t like them self (cannot fathom their pain) Thats where we as a community should step in to help. Support people, educate them that doctors are trying their level best, without giving up.

Doctors just have one plea to the rest of us, STAY HOME IF YOU CAN. 
The situation is only getting worse , register and get yourself VACCINATED. 
HELP people in need by donating and or directing them to the correct and verified info and medical help. 

(P.s To watch the entire video please go to @weareyuvaa page ) 
Credit : @weareyuvaa

latestPosts.caption:
Toughest week of my life. Lost a part of me. Time to rest baby boy ♥️🥺
Until we meet again super soon K’os ♾️ 
Thankyou for choosing us ! And being the most unconditional part of my life. Us against the world alwayssss ! 

My boy brought out the most humane side in me. If you know me you know K’os is my life. He never complained or troubled, Just sat by my side through every (and I mean every) sickness , sad day , bad day and happy day. I knew no matter what I have you. No judgements just unconditional love and acceptance.
Be it your bark when I come home or you stealing my pillow to wake me up in the morning, you made sure my day started and ended with you and I’d have it nooo other way. 
The most important part of my family.
And a part of every puja to party. 

Be well my puppy ♥️ I’m a mess without you :( I miss you! You’ll always be my sunshine. 

4.3.08 - 5.10.22 ♾️💞
